{"tid":1788343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冷氣軍師屌完行動手足未","createTime":"2019-12-18T14:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T03:19:42.000Z","uid":199926,"like":34,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"474fc16409b264abd127d400ad025d1d95a98839","tid":1788343,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"打爛交通燈又話唔對準政權<br />\n塞交通又話阻人返工擾民<br />\n裝修商場又問點解要咁做畫面唔好睇<br />\n影狗仔狗女相又話唔好搞到細路<br />\n連影藍絲大頭相都話批鬥 驚得罪所謂中立分子<br />\n仲未計以前瘋狂割火魔同私了手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我想講 手足每做一樣野都比你地係到鳩噏有用 多謝每一位行動手足 無論勇武定和理非</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每次見到壞咗交通燈都會覺得手足做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc4b48618eb89de550763ff498d2a02bdb77a09","tid":1788343,"uid":58967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:53:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d54f2e6a8be8d60444285e407448041ab5a3021","tid":1788343,"uid":58967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:53:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48c1b6a5a4c114f651a4cf993ada1f0c39f66ee9","tid":1788343,"uid":58967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:54:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4230c11a6054956645395a85751f15e3a6842247","tid":1788343,"uid":3172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:54:11.000Z","msg":"邊個會屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcb68271f6960a7c2920e6669e03f33f75f8380","tid":1788343,"uid":199926,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xbnqo7J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXbnqo7J.jpg&h=036d1080&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zuCaAeo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzuCaAeo.png&h=0f402c15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"078365000a9e7851a155d77b811a5821b295073